    "In this paper, we have sought to expand the review of GPT-4 and bring a range of disciplinary expertise to bear on its potential concerns, particularly for high-risk areas.",
    "In conducting this review, we also intend to point to the need for new forms of increased reflection on how LLMs are reviewed, by whom, what data reviewers need access to, and how concerns such as bias, harm, or risk are addressed.",
    "Digital Health | https://doi.org/10.1371/journal.pdig.0000417January 18, 2024"
